name: Charles CAMARDO v. John MORAN and the Superior Court of the State of Rhode Island

parties: Charles CAMARDO v. John MORAN and the Superior Court of the State of Rhode Island.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The petition for writ of habeas corpus is denied for lack of adequate supporting material.

attorneys: John F. Cicilline, Providence, for petitioner.
Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Alyssa L. Talanker, Sp. Asst. Atty. Gen., for respondents.
